, neutron stars, in the full theory of\ngeneral relativity, including a simple, yet effective treatment for the surface\nregion of the star (where the rest mass density is abruptly dropping to zero).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 1998 13:52:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
