 Finally, I discuss recent developments which may allow simulations of\nQCD with full chiral symmetry even at finite lattice spacing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 1998 06:50:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Nov 1998 01:14:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 1998 06:34:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
